---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — CosmoCrew"
  description="CosmoCrew builds calm, capable software, crafted to last, starting on iOS. Independent, craft-first, and just getting started."
  path="about"
>
  <section class="container narrow">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About CosmoCrew</h1>
    </div>

    <Prose>
      <p>
        CosmoCrew builds calm, capable software — whatever it&rsquo;s for.
        We&rsquo;re independent and move with intent: ship things we&rsquo;d use
        every day, sweat the details, and keep improving them long after launch.
      </p>
      <p>
        We believe a few genuinely good tools beat a pile of half-finished ones.
        So we stay focused — on craft, on speed, and on respecting your attention
        — and let quality set the pace.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>SliceFocus</strong> brings visual day planning and focus, and
        <strong>LexiPower</strong> sharpens vocabulary practice — both live on
        iOS today. Each one started as something we wanted for ourselves, and
        each keeps getting sharper.
      </p>
      <p>
        We&rsquo;re just getting started. If one of our apps has earned a place
        on your home screen, thank you — it genuinely means a lot. You can reach
        us anytime
        at <a href="mailto:contact@cosmocrew.dev">contact@cosmocrew.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </Prose>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .narrow {
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
</style>
